body:
Actually I can't find the symbol _ZNK6google8protobuf7Message11GetTypeNameEv in libtensorflow_framework.so, but I can find it in _pywrap_tensorflow_internal.so. Also including libtensorflow_framework.so and dlopen did't bring any results. In the meanwhile I switched to release 1.9 but the issue is still there. What if the problem is in _pywrap_tensorflow_internal.so? The error starts in 
`  File "/usr/lib/python3.5/imp.py", line 342, in load_dynamic
        return _load(spec)`
